Error[E413]: Top-Level Effect

Effectful operation is not allowed at top level (requires: IO).

  tests/fixtures/precedence/logical_precedence.flx:1:1
  |
1 | print(true || false && false);
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  | ------------------------------ top-level effectful expression

Hint:
  Move this code into `fn main() with ... { ... }`.


Error[E414]: Missing Main Function

