  tests/fixtures/precedence/logical_precedence.flx:1:1
  |
1 | print(true || false && false);
  | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  | ------------------------------ effectful top-level execution

Hint:
  Define `fn main() with ... { ... }` and move execution there.


